OL,5, When 10-month-old Colin Smith          
OL,6, contracted HIV after receiving         
OL,7, contaminated blood, his parents' house 
OL,8, was daubed with "Aids dead".           
OL,10,FHis father was also forced to leave his
OL,11,Fjob.                                   
OL,13,FNow 34 years on from his death from    
OL,14,FAids at the age of seven, his family   
OL,15,Fare facing another injustice.          
OL,17,FA BBC investigation has found Prof     
OL,18,FArthur Bloom, the doctor who gave Colin
OL,19,Finfected imported blood product Factor 
OL,20,FVIII, broke his own rules to do so.    
